metadata.name: Do you want to Change?
metadata.description:
Animal Crossing has brought that nostalgic feeling to us all. I was so inspired by the excitement and joy the game brings to my life. I couldn't resist drawing my character in those cute outfits that the able sisters sell.

"Do you want to Change" 

About this illustration:
Created by Auna Amire on June 28th-June 30th, 2020 (4 hours in total) 
Procreate
2160x2700 px
